The paper introduces a new programmer interface for functions in the dune module, which is a computational science and engineering library. Therefore, cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the implementation of run-time polymorphism, which is related to numerical analysis (cs.NA) and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of lambda expressions and return-by-value is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG).
